rd, but I want to ensure the implementation is clear and effective! Let’s keep pushing forward.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_JPq0C7rLk9NdFnIuLEq4Btp9|fc_0a3de1588402e5d80169f063c814488196928d26884d40a58c", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "git status --short && git log --oneline -5"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 539, "output": 1538, "cacheRead": 43008, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 45085, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777361842439, "responseId": "resp_0a3de1588402e5d80169f063b2e640819699ab474c4cd1b0d5"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_JPq0C7rLk9NdFnIuLEq4Btp9|fc_0a3de1588402e5d80169f063c814488196928d26884d40a58c", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "?? metadata/plexus/plexus-utils/1.0.2/\n174c09c044 (HEAD -> ai/add-lib-support-plexus-plexus-utils-1.0.2) Scaffold plexus:plexus-utils:1.0.2\nb6d4cb1bf9 (origin/master, origin/HEAD, master) [GenAI] Test fix for com.fasterxml.jackson.jr:jackson-jr-objects:2.17.0 using gpt-5.4 (#2485)\n8a02c973f6 [GenAI] Add support for org.osgi:org.osgi.namespace.extender:1.0.1 using gpt-5.5 (#2541)\n6d67278a7b [GenAI] Add support for org.eclipse.aether:aether-impl:1.0.2.v20150114 using gpt-5.5 (#2540)\n98b6da0ac3 [GenAI] Add support for org.osgi:org.osgi.resource:1.0.0 using gpt-5.5 (#2534)\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777361864447}]}
